  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 25 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 13 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 29</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, E, F, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique functions as Zanmaken Ni no Tachi, except that when the ray hits, it bounces to the nearest creature that meets its criteria, and will continue to bounce until there are no more available targets, until it has hit 1 target per 4 levels, or until it would deal no damage. The damage is rolled once. Each bounce, the damage is halved (rounded down). You must still make an attack roll for each bounce.<br><br>If a bounce misses, it will still bounce to another target. The ray will not bounce to creatures it has already (tried to) hit. The penalty to hit for passing through other creatures still applies.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to increase the damage by 1d6, up to 1d6 per level or 18d6 damage total, whichever is lower.</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
